name: Cash
description@id: Kas yang dimiliki perusahaan untuk operasi harian.

name: Petty Cash
description: Small cash fund for minor expenses
description@id: Dana kas kecil untuk pengeluaran minor.

name: Cash in Hand
description: Cash physically held at office or site
description@id: Kas yang secara fisik tersedia di kantor atau lokasi.

name: Bank Suspense
description: Temporary account for unclear bank transactions
description@id: Rekening sementara untuk transaksi bank yang tidak jelas.

name: Outstanding Receipts
description: Receivables expected but not yet collected
description@id: Piutang yang diharapkan namun belum diterima.

name: Outstanding Payments
description: Payables due but not yet paid
description@id: Utang yang jatuh tempo tetapi belum dibayar.

name: Account Receivable
description: Amounts owed by customers for sales
description@id: Jumlah yang terutang oleh pelanggan dari penjualan.

name: Account Receivable (PoS)
description@id: Piutang yang berasal dari transaksi Point-of-Sale.

name: Employee Liabilities
description@id: Jumlah yang terutang oleh karyawan (uang muka, pinjaman).

name: Other Inventory
description: Inventory items not classified under main stock
description@id: Persediaan yang tidak termasuk dalam kategori utama.

name: Building Rent
description: Prepaid rent for office or building facilities
description@id: Sewa gedung dibayar di muka untuk kantor atau fasilitas gedung.

name: Prepaid Insurance
description@id: Premi asuransi yang dibayar di muka.

name: Prepaid Tax PPh 21
description@id: Pajak penghasilan karyawan dibayar di muka (PPh 21).

name: Prepaid Tax PPh 25
description@id: Angsuran pajak penghasilan badan dibayar dimuka (PPh 25).

name: Prepaid Tax PPh 28A
description: Prepaid corporate tax on certain transactions (PPh 28A)
description@id: Pajak dibayar dimuka atas transaksi tertentu (PPh 28A).

name: Down Payment
description: Payments made in advance for goods or services
description@id: Pembayaran dimuka untuk barang atau jasa.

name: Buildings - Non-Permanent
description: Temporary structures or site offices - 10 Years.
description@id: Bangunan sementara atau direksi keet - 10 Tahun.

name: Furniture (Wood/Rattan)
description: Furniture made of wood or rattan (Group 1).

name: Furniture (Metal/Mixed)
description: Furniture made of metal or mixed materials (Group 2).

name: Accum. Depr. - Buildings Permanent
description: Contra account for Permanent Building depreciation.
description@id: Akun kontra untuk penyusutan Bangunan Permanen.

name: Accum. Depr. - Buildings Non-Permanent
description: Contra account for Non-Permanent Building depreciation.
description@id: Akun kontra untuk penyusutan Bangunan Non-Permanen.

name: Accum. Depr. - Motorcycles
description@id: Akun kontra untuk penyusutan Sepeda Motor.

name: Accum. Depr. - Operational Vehicles
description: Contra account for Operational Vehicles depreciation.
description@id: Akun kontra untuk penyusutan Kendaraan Operasional.

name: Accum. Depr. - Heavy Vehicles
description: Contra account for Heavy Vehicles depreciation.
description@id: Akun kontra untuk penyusutan Kendaraan Berat.

name: Accum. Depr. - IT Equipment
description: Contra account for IT Equipment depreciation.
description@id: Akun kontra untuk penyusutan Perlengkapan IT.

name: Accum. Depr. - Communication Devices
description: Contra account for Communication Devices depreciation.
description@id: Akun kontra untuk penyusutan Alat Komunikasi.

name: Accum. Depr. - Office Electronics
description: Contra account for Office Electronics depreciation.
description@id: Akun kontra untuk penyusutan Elektronik Kantor.

name: Accum. Depr. - Appliances
description@id: Akun kontra untuk penyusutan Peralatan Pantry.

name: Accum. Depr. - Furniture (Wood/Rattan)
description: Contra account for Wood/Rattan Furniture depreciation.
description@id: Akun kontra untuk penyusutan Perabot Kayu/Rotan.

name: Accum. Depr. - Furniture (Metal/Mixed)
description: Contra account for Metal/Mixed Furniture depreciation.
description@id: Akun kontra untuk penyusutan Perabot Logam/Campuran.

name: Accum. Depr. - Building Installations
description: Contra account for Building Installations depreciation.
description@id: Akun kontra untuk penyusutan Instalasi Gedung.

name: Accum. Depr. - Light Machinery
description: Contra account for Light Machinery depreciation.
description@id: Akun kontra untuk penyusutan Mesin Ringan.

name: Accum. Depr. - Heavy Machinery
description: Contra account for Heavy Machinery depreciation.
description@id: Akun kontra untuk penyusutan Mesin Berat.

name: Accum. Depr. - Heavy Construction Equip
description: Contra account for Heavy Construction Equipment depreciation.
description@id: Akun kontra untuk penyusutan Alat Berat Konstruksi.

name: Accum. Amortization - Software Licenses
description: Contra account for Software Licenses amortization.
description@id: Akun kontra untuk amortisasi Lisensi Software.

name: Funds in Transit
description@id: Dana yang sedang dipindahkan antar rekening.

name: Account Payable
description: Amounts owed to the company by customers
description@id: Jumlah yang terutang oleh pelanggan kepada perusahaan.

name: Shareholder Deposit
description@id: Setoran yang diterima dari pemegang saham.

name: Third-Party Deposit
description@id: Setoran yang diterima dari pihak ketiga.

name: Salary Deposit
description@id: Gaji yang harus dibayarkan kepada karyawan.

name: Tax Payable Pph 29
description: Corporate tax payable for the year (PPh 29)
description@id: Pajak badan terutang untuk tahun berjalan (PPh 29).

name: Accrued Payable Electricity
description: Electricity expenses accrued but not yet paid
description@id: Beban listrik yang terakru tetapi belum dibayar.

name: Accrued Payable Water
description: Water expenses accrued but not yet paid
description@id: Beban air yang terakru tetapi belum dibayar.

name: Accrued Payable Telp & Internet
description@id: Beban telepon dan internet yang terakru.

name: Accrued Payable Insurance
description@id: Premi asuransi yang terakru tetapi belum dibayar.

name: Advance Sales
description: Revenue received in advance from customers
description@id: Pendapatan yang diterima di muka dari pelanggan.

name: Interim Stock
description: Stock temporarily recorded during inventory processing
description@id: Stok yang dicatat sementara saat proses inventaris.

name: Paid Capital
description@id: Modal yang benar-benar disetor oleh pemegang saham.

name: Unpaid Capital
description: Capital committed but not yet paid by shareholders
description@id: Modal yang dijanjikan tetapi belum disetor oleh pemegang saham.

name: Prive (Personal Retrieval)
description@id: Penarikan dana oleh pemilik dari perusahaan.

name: Past Profit & Loss
description: Profit and loss carried over from previous periods
description@id: Laba dan rugi yang dibawa dari periode sebelumnya.

name: Ongoing Profit & Loss
description: Profit and loss for the current period
description@id: Laba dan rugi untuk periode berjalan.

name: Sales
description: Revenue from goods or services sold
description@id: Pendapatan dari barang atau jasa yang dijual.

name: Sales Discount
description: Discounts given to customers on sales
description@id: Diskon yang diberikan kepada pelanggan atas penjualan.

name: Cost of Goods Sold
description@id: Biaya langsung dari barang yang dijual.

name: Fees
description: General fees incurred by the company

name: Taxes
description: General taxes paid by the company

name: Office Services
description@id: Layanan yang digunakan dalam operasional kantor.

name: Vehicle Service
description: Maintenance and service costs for vehicles

name: Vehicle Parking & Toll Fee
description: Parking and toll fees for vehicles

name: Raw Materials
description: Expenses for raw materials used in production
description@id: Beban untuk bahan baku yang digunakan dalam produksi.

name: Stock Variation
description: Represents the difference in value between Opening Stock and Closing Stock for the period.
description@id: Mencerminkan selisih nilai antara Persediaan Awal dan Persediaan Akhir pada periode berjalan.

name: Studies & Works
description: Expenses related to studies or projects

name: Bar & Restaurant
description: Expenses for meals at bars and restaurants
description@id: Beban untuk makanan di bar dan restoran.

name: Food: Reception & Delivery
description: Food expenses for receptions and deliveries
description@id: Beban makanan untuk resepsi dan pengiriman.

name: Training and Documentation
description: Expenses for employee training and documentation
description@id: Beban untuk pelatihan karyawan dan dokumentasi.

name: Depreciation Exp - Buildings Permanent
description: Systematic allocation of the cost of long-term, durable structures (e.g., concrete/brick) over their useful life.
description@id: Alokasi sistematis atas biaya perolehan bangunan permanen (beton/bata) yang memiliki masa manfaat jangka panjang.

name: Depreciation Exp - Buildings Non-Permanent
description: Periodic expense for temporary or semi-permanent structures (e.g., sheds, containers) with a shorter lifespan.
description@id: Beban periodik untuk bangunan semi-permanen atau sementara (seperti bedeng atau kontainer) dengan masa manfaat pendek.

name: Depreciation Exp - Motorcycles
description: Depreciation of two-wheeled motorized vehicles used for business operations or delivery.
description@id: Penyusutan untuk kendaraan roda dua yang digunakan untuk operasional bisnis atau pengiriman.

name: Depreciation Exp - Operational Vehicles
description: Cost allocation for standard company cars, SUVs, and vans used for administrative and daily business tasks.
description@id: Alokasi biaya untuk kendaraan standar perusahaan seperti mobil dinas, SUV, atau van operasional.

name: Depreciation Exp - Heavy Vehicles
description: Depreciation for large-scale transport assets such as dump trucks, prime movers, or large buses.
description@id: Penyusutan untuk kendaraan angkutan berat seperti truk dump, truk trailer, atau bus besar.

name: Depreciation Exp - IT Equipment
description: Allocation of cost for computing hardware, including servers, laptops, desktops, and networking gear.
description@id: Alokasi biaya perangkat keras komputer, termasuk server, laptop, desktop, dan perangkat jaringan.

name: Depreciation Exp - Communication Devices
description: Periodic expense for mobile phones, PBX systems, and other telecommunications hardware.
description@id: Beban periodik untuk alat komunikasi seperti telepon seluler, sistem PBX, dan perangkat telekomunikasi lainnya.

name: Depreciation Exp - Office Electronics
description: Depreciation for office peripherals such as printers, scanners, photocopiers, and projectors.
description@id: Penyusutan untuk perangkat elektronik kantor seperti printer, scanner, mesin fotokopi, dan proyektor.

name: Depreciation Exp - Appliances
description: Cost allocation for utility equipment like refrigerators, microwaves, and air conditioning units.
description@id: Alokasi biaya untuk peralatan penunjang seperti kulkas, microwave, dispenser, dan unit AC.

name: Depreciation Exp - Furniture (Wood/Rattan)
description: Depreciation for furniture made primarily of organic materials, such as wooden desks and cabinets.
description@id: Penyusutan untuk furnitur yang berbahan dasar kayu atau rotan, seperti meja dan lemari kayu.

name: Depreciation Exp - Furniture (Metal/Mixed)
description: Depreciation for durable furniture like steel filing cabinets and metal-framed workstations.
description@id: Penyusutan untuk furnitur tahan lama berbahan logam atau campuran, seperti lemari arsip besi.

name: Depreciation Exp - Building Installations
description: Allocation of cost for integrated systems like electrical wiring, plumbing, and HVAC systems.
description@id: Alokasi biaya untuk instalasi bangunan seperti sistem kelistrikan, pemipaan (plumbing), dan sistem tata udara (HVAC).

name: Depreciation Exp - Light Machinery
description: Periodic expense for small-scale industrial tools, small generators, and portable equipment.
description@id: Beban periodik untuk mesin industri skala kecil, perkakas mesin, atau generator portabel.

name: Depreciation Exp - Heavy Machinery
description: Cost allocation for large-scale production lines, industrial plant machinery, and stationary power plants.
description@id: Alokasi biaya untuk mesin produksi skala besar, mesin pabrik, atau pembangkit listrik stasioner.

name: Depreciation Exp - Heavy Construction Equip
description: Depreciation for site-specific machinery like excavators, cranes, and bulldozers.
description@id: Penyusutan untuk alat berat konstruksi seperti ekskavator, crane, buldoser, dan mesin penggilas.

name: Amortization Exp - Software Licenses
description: Systematic write-off of the cost of intangible software assets and licenses over their legal or useful life.
description@id: Penghapusan biaya aset tak berwujud secara sistematis untuk lisensi perangkat lunak selama masa manfaatnya.

name: Foreign Exchange Gain
description@id: Keuntungan dari fluktuasi mata uang asing.

name: Gain on Sale of Fixed Assets
Interest Expense
description: Interest paid on loans and debts
description@id: Beban bunga atas pinjaman dan hutang.

name: Foreign Exchange Loss
description@id: Kerugian dari fluktuasi mata uang asing.

name: Loss on Sale of Fixed Assets
Cash Discount Loss
description: Loss due to cash discounts given
description@id: Kerugian akibat diskon kas yang diberikan.

name: Cash Discount Gain
description: Gain due to cash discounts received
description@id: Keuntungan akibat diskon kas yang diterima.

name: Undistributed Profits/Losses
description: Profits or losses not yet distributed
description@id: Laba atau rugi yang belum didistribusikan.
